                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-95-victim929 t18320405-95-viclabel602"></join>. On the 24th of February, about two o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18320405-95-crimeloc603">Fenchurch-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-95-crimeloc603" type="placeName" value="Fenchurch-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-95-crimeloc603" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-95-off600 t18320405-95-crimeloc603"></join>, I felt something at my pocket; I felt, and missed my handkerchief - I turned, and the prisoner was close at my left hand; I collared him, and he instantly threw my handkerchief behind him - I picked it up, and took him to the watch-house - this is it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-95-person931">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  FIGGINS
               <interp inst="t18320405-95-person931" type="surname" value="FIGGINS"></interp>
