                     <interp inst="t18320405-95-person931" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming from Aldgate. I saw the prisoner throw something behind him, which no doubt was the handkerchief - the prosecutor picked it up.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not pick the pocket; the handkerchief was thrown on the ground - I took it up; the gentleman turned, and seized me, and I threw it down.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
